<template>
  <v-card class="test">
    <v-card-title>
      {{nodeTitle}}
    </v-card-title>
    <template v-for="(prop, idx) in nodeProps">
      <v-card-text :key="idx">
        {{prop.name}}
      </v-card-text>
    </template>
  </v-card>
</template>

<script>
  export default {
    name: 'NodeInfo',
    props: [
      "node"
    ],
    data() {
      return {}
    },
    computed: {
      nodeTitle(){
        return this.node.title? this.node.title: this.node.id
      },
      nodeProps(){
        return this.node.props? this.node.props: [{name: 'other'}, {name: 'prop2'}, {name: 'prop3'}];
      }
    },
    mounted() {},
    methods: {}
  }
</script>

<!-- Add "scoped" attribute to limit CSS to this component only -->
<style lang="scss">
  .test{
    background-color: red;
    width: 200px;
  }
</style>
